MCMC: niter=300, nburnin=80, thin=1, nchains=1 \nFit\nUse summary() for posterior summaries; plot() for diagnostics; predict() for predictions.\n\n[treated]\nMixGPD fit | backend: Stick-Breaking Process | kernel: Amoroso Distribution | GPD tail: FALSE\nn = 268 | components = 6 | epsilon = 0.025\nMCMC: niter=300, nburnin=80, thin=1, nchains=1 \nFit\nUse summary() for posterior summaries; plot() for diagnostics; predict() for predictions.\n```\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\npred_mean_bulk <- predict(fit_sb_bulk, x = x_eval, type = \"mean\", interval = \"credible\", nsim_mean = 150)\nhead(pred_mean_bulk)\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\n  id    estimate     lower      upper ps\n1  1 23.16832666 0.7031016   9.183195 NA\n2  2  3.53218933 0.8367846   1.187504 NA\n3  3 -0.08630895 0.5969962  -2.255838 NA\n4  4 -0.61567447 0.5652148  -6.648651 NA\n5  5 -5.11201305 0.5384309 -13.148733 NA\n6  6  3.25110670 0.5799566  11.009501 NA\n```\n\n\n:::\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nplot(pred_mean_bulk)\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ex10-causal-x-no-ps-sb_files/figure-html/predict-mean-sb-bulk-1.png){width=768}\n:::\n\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ex10-causal-x-no-ps-sb_files/figure-html/predict-mean-sb-bulk-2.png){width=768}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\npred_q_bulk <- predict(fit_sb_bulk, x = x_eval, type = \"quantile\", p = 0.5, interval = \"credible\")\nhead(pred_q_bulk)\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\n  id index    estimate      lower    upper ps\n1  1   0.5   0.2424947  -3.701047 1.645206 NA\n2  2   0.5   0.3004401  -3.581150 1.589837 NA\n3  3   0.5  -0.3463646  -3.451886 1.116737 NA\n4  4   0.5  -0.9512494  -8.495398 1.046031 NA\n5  5   0.5 -10.3795024 -87.999989 1.329753 NA\n6  6   0.5  -0.2774799  -3.851546 1.081826 NA\n```\n\n\n:::\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nplot(pred_q_bulk)\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ex10-causal-x-no-ps-sb_files/figure-html/predict-quantile-sb-bulk-